%% aidea 自包含 .dmg GUI — 程序调用流程时序图
%% 覆盖：①首次启动拉起后端栈 ②Chat 本地 ③Chat 在线 ④模型后端切换 ⑤Quest/Comment ⑥健康概览(9090)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as 前端 (React)
    participant API as api/invoke.ts
    participant BOOT as bootstrap (Rust)
    participant PG as PostgreSQL (sidecar)
    participant OLL as Ollama (sidecar)
    participant SRV as aidea serve (sidecar, gRPC 50051)
    participant EXT as 在线厂商 (OpenAI 兼容)
    participant CORE as ide_core (进程内复用)

    Note over UI,PG: === ① 首次启动拉起后端栈（失败重试） ===
    UI->>API: 应用启动
    API->>BOOT: bootstrap_stack(VendorConfig)
    BOOT->>PG: initdb(AppData/pgdata) [首次] + pg_ctl start
    PG-->>BOOT: 就绪
    BOOT->>PG: createdb aidea + role + 应用 migrations/*.sql
    BOOT->>OLL: ollama serve 启动
    OLL-->>BOOT: 就绪
    BOOT->>OLL: ollama create nes-tab (FROM qwen2.5:0.5b 本地权重)
    OLL-->>BOOT: 模型就绪
    BOOT->>SRV: aidea serve 127.0.0.1:50051 (env: LLM/NES backend, KEY)
    loop 轮询 Health.Check
        BOOT->>SRV: HealthService.Check
        SRV-->>BOOT: SERVING
    end
    BOOT-->>API: emit("bootstrap-done")
    API-->>UI: BootstrapPage → 进入主界面

    Note over UI,SRV: === ② Chat（本地，后端路由 Ollama） ===
    UI->>API: chat_send({session_id,message})
    API->>SRV: AgentService.Chat (gRPC stream)
    SRV->>OLL: /api/chat (nes-tab:latest)
    OLL-->>SRV: tokens
    SRV-->>API: emit("chat-token"×N) → emit("chat-done")
    API-->>UI: 流式渲染

    Note over UI,EXT: === ③ Chat（在线，Key 留后端） ===
    UI->>API: chat_send({session_id,message})
    API->>SRV: AgentService.Chat (gRPC stream)
    Note right of SRV: serve 持 AIDEA_LLM_API_KEY，调 EXT
    SRV->>EXT: POST {base_url}/v1/chat/completions (Bearer Key)
    EXT-->>SRV: tokens
    SRV-->>API: emit("chat-token"×N) → emit("chat-done")
    API-->>UI: 流式渲染（前端不接触 Key）

    Note over UI,SRV: === ④ 模型后端切换（重启 serve） ===
    UI->>API: set_vendor_config({kind:"online",base_url})
    API->>BOOT: 停旧 aidea serve
    BOOT->>SRV: SIGTERM
    BOOT->>SRV: 以新 env 重启 aidea serve (AIDEA_LLM_BACKEND=openai, KEY from keyring)
    loop 轮询 Health.Check
        BOOT->>SRV: Check
    end
    BOOT-->>API: emit("vendor-changed")
    API-->>UI: 状态转绿

    Note over UI,CORE: === ⑤ Quest / Comment（进程内 ide-core） ===
    UI->>API: quest_run({goal})
    API->>CORE: Quest::run(goal, CoreConfig)
    CORE-->>API: QuestReport
    API-->>UI: 列表+详情
    UI->>API: comment_add({file,line,text})
    API->>CORE: CommentStore.add (直连 bundled PG)
    CORE-->>API: id
    API-->>UI: 刷新

    Note over UI,SRV: === ⑥ 健康概览（拉 9090，复用数据不内嵌） ===
    UI->>API: fetch_health()
    API->>SRV: GET :9090/healthz + /console
    SRV-->>API: "ok\n" + 文本+--- json ---+JSON
    API-->>UI: HealthOverview 渲染
